---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Food & Beverage E-Commerce Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North" description="Drive subscriptions, replenishment, and repeat purchases with engaging content and timely reminders.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/ecommerce-retail/food-beverage" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Food & Beverage
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Food & Beverage</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">13 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Food & Beverage Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Drive subscriptions, replenishment, and repeat purchases with engaging content and timely reminders.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Food and beverage brands live or die by repeat purchases. Consumable products should mean predictable revenue—but only if you have systems to drive reorders.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Subscription Conversion</h2>

          <p>
            Most customers want to try before they subscribe. Post-purchase sequences that convert satisfied one-time buyers into subscribers are essential for predictable revenue.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Replenishment Reminders</h2>

          <p>
            Know how long products typically last. Send reminders before customers run out—when they're ready to buy, not when they've already bought from someone else.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Recipe & Usage Content</h2>

          <p>
            Keep customers engaged with recipes and usage ideas. Products sitting unused in pantries don't get reordered. Inspiration drives consumption and reorders.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-red-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Brand?</h3>
            <p class="text-orange-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your food & beverage brand.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-orange-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
